	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Jul</p>
			<p class="post-day">24</p>
			<p class="post-year">2003</p>				
		</div>

		AOL hired John McKinley, former CTO of Merrill Lynch, as its new Chief Technology Strategist and President of AOL Technologies. At Merrill, McKinley was a visible and respected leader in the move to Web services. Hiring him suggests that AOL, which has always defined itself as a company that doesn&#8217;t care about technology, may be changing its tune. The Internet companies that have thrived while AOL faltered &#8212; Microsoft, Amazon.com, ...
		
	</div>

	<div class="post-footer">
