</div>

<div id="post-834" class="cf post-834 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2003/07/controversy-isnt-the-same-as-power/" title="Controversy isn&#039;t the same as power" rel="bookmark">Controversy isn&#039;t the same as power</a>
		
