			<p class="post-day">21</p>
			<p class="post-year">2003</p>				
		</div>

		Cindy Skrzycki of the Washington Post, quoted in Fortune: &quot;[R]ight now I think the most powerful agency is the FCC, with its recent decision [to relax media concentration rules].&quot;
		
	</div>

	<div class="post-footer">
